ion enacted in 2023 paved the way for the utilization of AI video surveillance during the trial period encompassing the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9386936274491418, \"rank\": 0.04609743400463835, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.799756870770666e-26, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"the utilization\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"the trial period\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This innovative approach employs algorithmic video surveillance, utilizing computer software to analyze real-time images captured by surveillance cameras.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This innovative approach\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"algorithmic video surveillance\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"computer software\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 677}, {\"ngram\": \"real-time images\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"surveillance cameras\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four prominent companies - Videtics, Orange Business, ChapsVision, and Wintics - have spearheaded the development of AI software, employing sophisticated algorithms to detect potential threats and abnormal behavior in public spaces.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 777, \"en